    public class PGDImpl
extends SFImpl
implements PGD
    An implementation of the model object 'PGD'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Xpg Base
    • Ypg Base
    • Xpg Units
    • Ypg Units
    • Xpg Size
    • Ypg Size
    • Reserved
    • Triplets
